  ],
  "remarks": "Texel F.C.G. Technology Ltd is a company based in Israel and run by Mark Blatt, an individual facilitating sanctions circumvention by providing the Russian defence and security industry with foreign sensitive electronics, including equipment originating in the Union, used to develop weapons used in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Therefore, Texel F.C.G. Technology Ltd is significantly frustrating the provisions against the circumvention of the provisions of Decision 2014/512/CFSP and Regulation (EU) No 833/2014 and is supporting Russia’s military and industrial complex.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}